com.fiu_CaSPR.Frank.Utility

Class FacebookPostThread

  • java.lang.Object
    • <any>
      • com.fiu_CaSPR.Frank.Utility.FacebookPostThread

  • public class FacebookPostThread
extends <any>
    Created by frankhu on 6/17/15. This Thread Class is used in order to send the post to Facebook in a background thread. We execute this thread in the PostActivity and when it has finished we want the postActivity to close, so we end the activity on post execute.
